<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 10:07:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>照片中：以色列现实的边缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-photos-on-the-edge-of-israels-reality/00000190-f88c-df0c-ab98-ffbf37680000</link><description>那是三月初——距离我父亲去世那一天是我一生中最可怕的一天已有两周了。库姆兰的宁静之旅</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 09:24:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-photos-on-the-edge-of-israels-reality/00000190-f88c-df0c-ab98-ffbf37680000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部12名儿童被杀，但内塔尼亚胡并不着急</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/12-children-killed-in-northern-israel-but-as-far-as-netanyahus-concerned-theres-no-rush/00000190-f838-d541-adbc-f9f844a40000</link><description>一个正在“七条战线”作战并出国旅行一周（包括一次特别的周末停留）的国家的元首根本不是一个领导人。他会的</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 08:13:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/12-children-killed-in-northern-israel-but-as-far-as-netanyahus-concerned-theres-no-rush/00000190-f838-d541-adbc-f9f844a40000</guid></item><item><title>数千人参加以色列北部火箭袭击中丧生的儿童和青少年的葬礼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/12-children-and-teens-killed-in-north-israel-rocket-strike-to-be-laid-to-rest/00000190-f7ed-d469-a39d-f7ff90670000</link><description>其中 11 名遇难者被埋葬在真主党火箭周六袭击的 Majdal Shams ■ 另一名遇难者被安葬在恩钦亚 ■ 28 人仍在医院接受治疗</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 06:37:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/12-children-and-teens-killed-in-north-israel-rocket-strike-to-be-laid-to-rest/00000190-f7ed-d469-a39d-f7ff90670000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/00000190-f7ca-d469-a39d-f7df6c950000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布一周前被反坦克火力击伤的尤纳坦·阿哈龙·格林布拉特中士死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 05:38:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/00000190-f7ca-d469-a39d-f7df6c950000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长：真主党将为迈季代勒沙姆斯致命袭击“付出代价”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article-live/u-s-condemns-horrific-attack-reportedly-highly-concerned-over-all-out-war/00000190-f724-d469-a39d-f7b7cff70000</link><description>真主党火箭袭击以色列 Majdal Shams 造成 12 名儿童和青少年死亡 ■ 以色列国防军宣布，以色列士兵在上周加沙战斗中受伤身亡 ■ 黎巴嫩报道：以色列在提尔北部和黎巴嫩南部发动一系列袭击 ■ 伊朗外交部警告关于在黎巴嫩任何新的“以色列冒险” ■ 以色列外交部发言人：“真主党是对昨天的大屠杀明确负责的实体”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 02:40:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article-live/u-s-condemns-horrific-attack-reportedly-highly-concerned-over-all-out-war/00000190-f724-d469-a39d-f7b7cff70000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在华盛顿的胜利并不能抵消他的惨重损失</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wins-in-washington-dont-cancel-out-his-heavy-losses/00000190-f66b-d541-adbc-fffb226c0000</link><description>尽管内塔尼亚胡在椭圆形办公室合影并在国会获得掌声，但许多关键问题仍未解决——尤其是人质交易——并且与卡马拉·哈里斯爆发了激烈的争执</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 23:49:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wins-in-washington-dont-cancel-out-his-heavy-losses/00000190-f66b-d541-adbc-fffb226c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和真主党比以往任何时候都更接近全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-risks-full-scale-escalation-with-hezbollah-while-still-wrangling-on-gaza-front/00000190-f5cb-dda7-a9f7-f7ff03d80000</link><description>周六，以色列在北部玩的俄罗斯轮盘赌在马贾勒沙姆斯失败了，当时真主党对以色列对其特工的袭击做出了回应。由于坚持延长华盛顿之行，内塔尼亚胡总理只能远程参加防务磋商</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 21:59:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-risks-full-scale-escalation-with-hezbollah-while-still-wrangling-on-gaza-front/00000190-f5cb-dda7-a9f7-f7ff03d80000</guid></item><item><title>为内塔尼亚胡欢呼的参议员和国会议员感到羞耻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/shame-on-the-senators-and-congressmen-who-cheered-netanyahu/00000190-f554-dda7-a9f7-f777bd370000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 21:33:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/shame-on-the-senators-and-congressmen-who-cheered-netanyahu/00000190-f554-dda7-a9f7-f777bd370000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：真主党将付出前所未有的代价；最高部长呼吁暗杀纳斯鲁拉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/netanyahu-hezbollah-will-pay-unprecedented-price-top-minister-calls-to-kill-nasrallah/00000190-f5ca-d8b8-a59a-fdde66be0000</link><description>真主党否认对以色列北部德鲁兹城镇发动致命袭击负责，该袭击造成 12 名儿童和青少年死亡。白宫谴责这起“可怕”的袭击，而以色列北部当地领导人要求立即采取军事回应</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 20:57:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/netanyahu-hezbollah-will-pay-unprecedented-price-top-minister-calls-to-kill-nasrallah/00000190-f5ca-d8b8-a59a-fdde66be0000</guid></item><item><title>“孩子们来玩，爆炸将他们撕成碎片”：目击者讲述了令人痛心的 Majdal Shams 袭击事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/children-came-to-play-and-an-explosion-shredded-them-to-pieces/00000190-f596-d8b8-a59a-fd9e0e080000</link><description>到达造成 11 名儿童和青少年死亡的罢工现场的 Majdal Shams 和附近村庄的居民报告说，爆炸发生在警报响起几秒钟后。 ,地上有受伤和死亡的儿童。这让我想起了 10 月 7 日。”一位居民说道</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 20:30:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/children-came-to-play-and-an-explosion-shredded-them-to-pieces/00000190-f596-d8b8-a59a-fd9e0e080000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩火箭袭击以色列戈兰高地，造成 12 名儿童和青少年死亡；以色列国防军指责真主党</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/11-children-teens-killed-and-dozens-wounded-in-rocket-strike-on-majdal-shams/00000190-f54a-d298-a592-fd7bffe80000</link><description>以色列医疗部门表示，此次袭击袭击了一个正在玩耍的儿童足球场，共有 29 人受伤。以色列国防军指责真主党发动了这次袭击，此前以色列对四名特工发动了袭击。现场的一名医生回忆道，“所有受害者都是 8 至 14 岁的儿童，都穿着运动服”</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 19:09:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/11-children-teens-killed-and-dozens-wounded-in-rocket-strike-on-majdal-shams/00000190-f54a-d298-a592-fd7bffe80000</guid></item><item><title>法院以“危害安全”为由延长半岛电视台在以色列的广播禁令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/court-extends-al-jazeera-broadcasting-ban-in-israel-citing-harm-to-security/00000190-f54f-d541-adbc-fdffd24b0000</link><description>该禁令是根据议会五月通过的一项法律发布的，该法律允许半岛电视台停止从以色列进行广播。法官表示，他已经看到证据证明该电视台播放的内容煽动恐怖袭击</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 18:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/court-extends-al-jazeera-broadcasting-ban-in-israel-citing-harm-to-security/00000190-f54f-d541-adbc-fdffd24b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队无人机袭击约旦河西岸纳布卢斯巴勒斯坦武装分子，17岁青年被打死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-drone-targets-palestinian-militants-in-west-banks-nablus-17-year-old-killed/00000190-f527-d45d-a5b3-ffaf9d060000</link><description>军方表示，纳布卢斯巴拉塔难民营的袭击目标是武装武装分子，造成一人死亡、多人受伤。以色列安全部门消息人士称，这是对当天早上针对以色列国防军士兵的枪击事件的回应</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 17:48:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-drone-targets-palestinian-militants-in-west-banks-nablus-17-year-old-killed/00000190-f527-d45d-a5b3-ffaf9d060000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事，第 295 天：来自黎巴嫩的火箭弹在以色列北部迈季代勒沙姆斯造成 9 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-295-rocket-fire-from-lebanon-kills-nine-in-north-israels-majdal-shams/00000190-f4af-dda7-a9f7-f7bfb5bd0000</link><description>戈兰高地 Majdal Shams 镇遭火箭弹袭击，造成 9 名以色列人死亡，伤亡人数最多的是儿童和青少年 ■ 巴勒斯坦人称，以色列国防军的袭击导致汗尤尼斯 (Khan Yunis) 23 人死亡，代尔巴拉学校 (Deir al-Balah) 至少 30 人死亡；以色列国防军：哈马斯利用学校作为指挥中心 ■ 以色列代表团下周前往罗马进行协议谈判 ■ 以色列国防军士兵在检查站受伤；巴勒斯坦卫生部门消息来源：随后的以色列国防军无人机袭击和约旦河西岸冲突导致 17 岁儿童死亡、28 人受伤 ■ 以下是战争进入 295 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 17:16:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-295-rocket-fire-from-lebanon-kills-nine-in-north-israels-majdal-shams/00000190-f4af-dda7-a9f7-f7bfb5bd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列向调解人提出新的加沙协议立场；官员警告称这可能会给谈判带来风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-presents-new-gaza-deal-position-to-mediators-officials-warn-it-could-risk-talks/00000190-f4f3-dda7-a9f7-f7f703420000</link><description>据以色列外交消息人士称，内塔尼亚胡坚持建立一个机制，阻止巴勒斯坦武装人员从加沙南部进入北部，尽管有人警告称这将危及与哈马斯的谈判</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 17:03:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-presents-new-gaza-deal-position-to-mediators-officials-warn-it-could-risk-talks/00000190-f4f3-dda7-a9f7-f7f703420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人集会，家人称内塔尼亚胡正在积极阻止人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-say-netanyahu-is-deliberately-obstructing-release-deal/00000190-f4ff-dda7-a9f7-f7ff6a350000</link><description>&amp;#39;一切都准备好了，可以继续前进。 “只有内塔尼亚胡在继续破坏这笔交易”，一名人质的母亲说道；以色列最大的城市和数十个地点都发生抗议活动</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 16:57:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-say-netanyahu-is-deliberately-obstructing-release-deal/00000190-f4ff-dda7-a9f7-f7ff6a350000</guid></item><item><title>“因为我们是左派”：在加沙，一名人质预测内塔尼亚胡将推迟迅速释放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/were-leftists-in-gaza-a-hostage-said-swift-release-was-unlikely-due-to-netanyahu/00000190-f46d-d8b8-a59a-fcff2d880000</link><description>在接受以色列第 12 频道采访时，被释放的人质阿迪娜·莫什 (Adina Moshe) 讲述了查姆·佩里 (Chaim Peri) 在被囚禁期间对她说的话，并描述了一名反抗议者如何在人质交易集会上咒骂她。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 15:57:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/were-leftists-in-gaza-a-hostage-said-swift-release-was-unlikely-due-to-netanyahu/00000190-f46d-d8b8-a59a-fcff2d880000</guid></item><item><title>当地卫生官员称，以色列对加沙中部和南部的空袭造成 50 多人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/health-officials-over-50-killed-in-israeli-airstrikes-in-central-and-southern-gaza/00000190-f45d-d298-a592-fc7f96c30000</link><description>以色列国防军袭击了代尔巴拉赫的一所学校大院，声称这是哈马斯的设施，导致在那里避难的 30 多名巴勒斯坦人被杀。据哈马斯管理的卫生部门称，早先在汗尤尼斯发生的一系列空袭已造成 23 人死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 14:01:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/health-officials-over-50-killed-in-israeli-airstrikes-in-central-and-southern-gaza/00000190-f45d-d298-a592-fc7f96c30000</guid></item><item><title>“我们不必靠刀剑生存”：为什么为和平而战的以色列和巴勒斯坦妇女没有失去希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ten-years-on-israeli-and-palestinian-women-are-still-fighting-for-peace/00000190-ea6a-d8b8-a59a-eefe070c0000</link><description>妇女工资和平组织是在一场加沙战争的阴影下成立的，并在迄今为止最血腥的一场战争中纪念其成立十周年。该组织认为，其加拿大裔以色列联合创始人维维安·西尔弗 (Vivian Silver) 于 10 月 7 日去世，加沙一个巴勒斯坦姐妹组织的多达 40 名成员的死亡只会强调任务的紧迫性</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 11:18:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ten-years-on-israeli-and-palestinian-women-are-still-fighting-for-peace/00000190-ea6a-d8b8-a59a-eefe070c0000</guid></item><item><title>“对以色列科学的战略打击”：领先学术机构的海外学生数量急剧下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/strategic-blow-leading-israeli-academic-institutions-see-sharp-fall-in-foreign-students/00000190-e55e-d59e-a1f5-ffdea7d70000</link><description>加沙战争后，魏茨曼科学研究所和特拉维夫大学的国际博士生和博士后学生数量急剧下降，科学家们现在担心以色列可能会变成像中国或伊朗一样的单一文化国家</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 09:11:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/strategic-blow-leading-israeli-academic-institutions-see-sharp-fall-in-foreign-students/00000190-e55e-d59e-a1f5-ffdea7d70000</guid></item></channel></rss>